quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  85,1,"The heaven, possessor of Buruj, acts as a witness"
  85,2,and the Promised Day
  85,3,"and one who witnesses, and what has been witnessed"
  85,4,Stand condemned the people (who acted as perpetrators) of the sites of the ditches and trenches
  85,5,(They arranged) the fire fed with abundant fuel (of alive Believers who refused to submit to illegitimate gods)
  85,6,"When those (perpetrators), alongside that (are) in sitting position (as executioners and spectators)"
  85,7,"And they, over what they do with the Believers, are witnesses"
  85,8,"And they did not take revenge from them except (for the reason) that they will continue to Believe in Allah, the All-Mighty, Worthy of Praise"
  85,9,"That One: for Him is the Dominion of the heavens and the earth. And Allah is Witness over all things"
  85,10,"Verily, those who had put into torture the Believing males and the Believing females, and then did not turn in repentance — then for them is the punishment of Hell, and for them is the punishment of Al-Hariq (the blazing-Fire of Hell)"
  85,11,"Verily, those who accepted Faith and performed righteous deeds: for them are Gardens, flow from underneath them rivers. That (becomes) the supreme success"
  85,12,"Verily, the Grip (of retribution) of your Nourisher-Sustainer is indeed very, very strict"
  85,13,"Surely He, He initiates (a creation) and shall (afterwards) resurrect"
  85,14,"And He is the Oft-Forgiving, the Most Loving One"
  85,15,"Owner of the Throne, the Glorious"
  85,16,Fully Capable of doing what He intends
  85,17,Has (the) Hadees of the forces reached you —
  85,18,(the forces) of Firaun and Samud
  85,19,Nay! Those who have disbelieved (persist) in (the) denial
  85,20,"And Allah, from beyond their limits is All-Surveillant (over them)"
  85,21,Of course! That is a Glorious Quran
  85,22,(inscribed) in Al-Lawh-al-Mahfuz (the Preserved Tablet)